# An early proposed name for parts of [[Victoria]] ([[Australia]]) explored by [[w:Thomas Mitchell|Thomas Mitchell]] (1792-1855), Latin for “Fortunate Australia” or “Happy Australia”. [http://www.whitehat.com.au/Australia/History/PlaceNames.asp]
